<Content>A bad experience The hotel is not in the center of the city and the rooms are too small, but the worst thing was a parking problem that nearly ruin our trip. When we got to there, we could not find place in the parking of the hotel, and the receptionist told us to park the car outside in the street. So we did it. The next morning, when we left the hotel to go to the airport , we could not find our car. It has been towed away. Parking was not allowed there , the traffic sign was not visible enough. So we had to go as fast as possible to collect the car and pay a fine. We got late to the airport and we were about to miss our flight to Roma. In summary, the hotel is far away from the tourist center, the rooms are small, and the staff is not helpful. It is not a place I would recommend. 
