<Content>Well worth a stay I stayed at the hotel albeniz for three nights in Feb. 2004 with my husband. It is a lovely hotel. Spotlessly clean, the room was very comfortable. Room service was excellent, fresh towels daily. Breakfast choice very good.A little far from the centre but near the Metro station clot. While we were in barcelona we were victims of a scam. Some substance was thrown from above on to us and a very well dressed pleasant man helped us wipe ourselves and kindly pickpocketed my husband of his wallet!! Watch out if you are going to visit Barcelona. The Manger of the albeniz was very helpful to us and we were very impressed by the concern of the hotel. Well recommended. We also loved Barcelona and wouldn't be put off going again. 
